title: Virtual CD 5.03 (CD,ISO,DVD)
description:
Virtual CD 5.03 creates CD/DVD images which can be edited and played on its virtual CD/DVD rom drive. It also plays .ISO images as if inserted into a physical drive.
Yeah it's an older version so it reqires no hacking or live activation, only a key. It's light and powerful and runs perfectly on 32 bit XP sp3 plus all previous Win OS's. I like it for these reasons and thought maybe you would too.
